name: Zillow Home Value Index (Zip Codes): Three Bedroom Homes - 65604,Ash Grove,MO
description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of three bedroom homes within the zip code of 65604, Ash Grove, MO. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
